{"tid":1055383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡姓副校長行事為人與校長相若 校內老師：俾佢帶領只會喺傷口上灑鹽","createTime":"2019-03-10T13:45:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T15:40:46.000Z","uid":52651,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"587d80fadde4a68d95e0ce925eb16db88dbaead9","tid":1055383,"uid":52651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T13:45:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190310/59353570?fbclid=IwAR3-7MfhnjmO5Enwx-5i8VEYNRXXZBeg7y2dQwa6lTczSrt1EMQCp-s35aU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190310%2F59353570%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3-7MfhnjmO5Enwx-5i8VEYNRXXZBeg7y2dQwa6lTczSrt1EMQCp-s35aU&d=NaAPOzxPFgptGlwmNixMNxPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=30853216\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190310%2F59353570%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3-7MfhnjmO5Enwx-5i8VEYNRXXZBeg7y2dQwa6lTczSrt1EMQCp-s35aU&h=67423043\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190310/59353570?fbclid=IwAR3-7MfhnjmO5Enwx-5i8VEYNRXXZBeg7y2dQwa6lTczSrt1EMQCp-s35aU</a><br />\n<br />\n李東海小學校長羅婉儀即日起請病假，其職務將由兩名副校長暫代。但《蘋果》據悉，其中一位副校長蔡淑萍同樣備受校內老師質疑。今日東華三院董事局與校內老師會面時，有老師斥其行事為人處事與羅相若，同樣沒有同理心。更有與蔡共事多年的老師直言︰「俾佢（蔡淑萍）帶領，（佢）只會喺老師傷口上面灑鹽。」"},{"pid":"89fd91ce426db4fed25f84a932aec341b667d5b3","tid":1055383,"uid":220701,"like":78,"dislike":0,"score":78,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T13:46:11.000Z","msg":"睇個勢似乎要將成間學校剷起"},{"pid":"b8a3519054395843d5218f2446e9be8bbf50c7d2","tid":1055383,"uid":37723,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T13:47:00.000Z","msg":"今次真係要出動坦克車同防暴警察 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6682ebea8f4b70ca400644b7d59180286691dd","tid":1055383,"uid":52651,"like":0,"dislike":46,"score":-46,"quote":{"pid":"89fd91ce426db4fed25f84a932aec341b667d5b3","tid":1055383,"uid":220701,"like":78,"dislike":0,"score"